{"url":"https://www.career-tasu.co.jp/recruit/","html":"\r\n<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"ja\">\r\n<head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\">\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Style-Type\" content=\"text/css\">\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Script-Type\" content=\"text/javascript\">\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Language\" content=\"ja\">\r\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0\">\r\n<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\r\n<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"株式会社キャリタス,採用情報,新卒採用\">\r\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"株式会社キャリタスの新卒採用情報を掲載しています。\">\r\n<title>新卒採用 | 株式会社キャリタス</title>\r\n<link rel=\"icon\" href=\"../favicon.ico\">\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" href=\"assets/css/styles.css\" media=\"all\">\r\n<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"assets/css/swiper-bundle.min.css\" />\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\">\r\n<link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin>\r\n<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=M+PLUS+1:wght@100..900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@100..900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\r\n<script src=\"assets/js/jquery.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"assets/js/jq-lib.js\"></script>\r\n<script src=\"https://para-com.jp/widget.js\" data-hid=\"46d4237e-ad1a-4eee-be62-b6c57a424b63\"></script>\r\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\r\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-5W1ZTEMJJY\"></script>\r\n<script>\r\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\r\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\r\n  gtag('js', new Date());\r\n\r\n  gtag('config', 'G-5W1ZTEMJJY');\r\n</script>\r\n<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://recruit.career-tasu.co.jp/newgraduate/\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"新卒採用 | 株式会社キャリタス\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"株式会社キャリタスの新卒採用情報を掲載しています。\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\" 株式会社キャリタス\" />\r\n<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://recruit.career-tasu.co.jp/newgraduate/assets/img/ogp.jpg\" />\r\n</head>\r\n<body id=\"index\">\r\n  <header>\r\n    <div class=\"inner c-flex__sb\">\r\n      <p id=\"logo\"><a href=\"./\"><img src=\"assets/img/h_logo.png\" alt=\"株式会社キャリタス\"></a></p>\r\n      <div id=\"btns\" class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n        <ul class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n          <li><a href=\"https://mypage.3070.i-webs.jp/rec_ct2027/\" target=\"_blank\">新卒ENTRY／MY PAGE</a></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n        <p><a href=\"https://landing.lineml.jp/r/1599619341-oVQDY4wO?lp=jM9O73\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"./assets/img/line.png\" alt=\"LILNE 友だち追加\"></a></p>\r\n        <div id=\"menuBtn\"><img src=\"./assets/img/menu.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </header>\r\n\r\n  \r\n  <div id=\"op\">\r\n    <div class=\"inner\">\r\n      <h1><img src=\"assets/img/index/h1.png\" alt=\"\"></h1>\r\n      <div id=\"ff_a\">\r\n        <p id=\"ffb1\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b1.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffb2\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b2.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffb3\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b3.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffb4\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b4.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffb5\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b5.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffb6\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_b6.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa1\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a1.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa2\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a2.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa3\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a3.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa4\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a4.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa5\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a5.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa6\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a6.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa7\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a7.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa8\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a8.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa9\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a9.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa10\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a10.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa11\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a11.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        <p id=\"ffa12\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff_a12.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n\r\n  <main>\r\n    <section id=\"message\">\r\n      <div class=\"inner\">\r\n        <h2><img src=\"assets/img/index/ttl_message.png\" alt=\"\"></h2>\r\n        <div class=\"text\">\r\n          <p>学ぶこと・働くことは人を成長させ、<br>\r\n            キャリア、そして人生を形成する。<br>\r\n            私たちキャリタスでは、<br>\r\n            この学ぶ・働く領域において新たな可能性を探り、<br>\r\n            「挑戦したい」「解決したい」という想いが集まって、<br>\r\n            一人ひとりのキャリアや社会の未来を<br>\r\n            より豊かにするためのプラス（＋）をうみだしています。<br>\r\n            次は、どんなプラス（＋）をうみだそう？</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/img_message.png\" alt=\"\"></p>  \r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"about\">\r\n      <div class=\"inner c-flex__sb\">\r\n        <div class=\"ff\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff1.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n        <div class=\"text\">\r\n          <h2>\r\n            <img src=\"assets/img/index/ttl_about.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            <span>会社を知る</span>\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            創業50年以上の歴史の中で培ってきた経験とノウハウを武器に、「進学」から「就職」に至るまでキャリタス[career+]を起点とした幅広いサービスを展開しています。\r\n          </p>\r\n          <ul class=\"pc\">\r\n            <li><a href=\"about/message.html\" class=\"btn\">トップメッセージ／経営理念</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"about/business.html\" class=\"btn\">事業紹介</a></li>\r\n          </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_about.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n\r\n      </div>\r\n      <ul class=\"sp\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"about/message.html\" class=\"btn\">トップメッセージ／経営理念</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"about/business.html\" class=\"btn\">事業紹介</a></li>\r\n      </ul>\r\n</section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"jobPeople\">\r\n      <div class=\"inner\">\r\n        <div class=\"ff\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff2.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n        <div class=\"ff ff3\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff3.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n        <h2>\r\n          <img src=\"assets/img/index/ttl_jobpeople.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n          <span>仕事と人を知る</span>\r\n        </h2>\r\n        <p class=\"h2f\">それぞれの職種で、様々な想いを持って日々働いている社員をご紹介します。</p>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"box\">\r\n          <div class=\"boxttl\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              <span>職種紹介</span>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n            <div class=\"text\">\r\n              <p>当社には様々な部署や職種があります。ここではその一部をご紹介します！</p>\r\n              <p class=\"pc\">\r\n                <a href=\"job-people/work.html\" class=\"btn\">職種紹介</a>\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_job.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <p class=\"sp\">\r\n          <a href=\"job-people/work.html\" class=\"btn\">職種紹介</a>\r\n        </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n        <div class=\"box box2\">\r\n          <div class=\"boxttl\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              <span>社員インタビュー</span>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n            <div class=\"text\">\r\n              <p>仕事のやりがいや入社理由、どのような成長ができるか、ご覧ください。</p>\r\n              <p class=\"pc\">\r\n                <a href=\"job-people/movie.html\" class=\"btn\">社員インタビュー</a>\r\n              </p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_movie.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <p class=\"sp\">\r\n            <a href=\"job-people/movie.html\" class=\"btn\">社員インタビュー</a>\r\n          </p>\r\n    </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"box box3\">\r\n          <div class=\"boxttl\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              <span>想いがつどう<br class=\"brsp\">プロジェクトストーリー</span>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n            <div class=\"text\">\r\n              <p>想いがつどい、より良いプラス（+）をうみだすため挑戦し続けるプロジェクトをご紹介します。</p>\r\n              <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/sc.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"swiper slider2\">\r\n              <div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\r\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                  <a href=\"job-people/project01.html\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ps01.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\r\n                  <a href=\"job-people/project02.html\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ps02.png\" alt=\"\"></a>\r\n                </div>\r\n              </div>\r\n              <div class=\"swiper-button-prev swiper-button-black\"></div>\r\n\t\t\t\t      <div class=\"swiper-button-next swiper-button-white\"></div>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"box box2 member\">\r\n          <div class=\"boxttl\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              <span>日本全国地域をプラス（＋）にする<br class=\"brsp\">メンバー紹介</span>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n            <div class=\"text\">\r\n              <p>全国各地で活躍する社員がこれまで経験してきたストーリーや、その拠点の特徴・雰囲気などをご紹介します。皆さんがお住まいの地域にも当社のビジネスは息づいています。</p>\r\n              <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/sc2.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_member.png\" alt=\"\"><a href=\"job-people/member.html\" class=\"btn\">日本全国地域を＋にするメンバー紹介</a></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n\r\n        <div class=\"box box3 career\">\r\n          <div class=\"boxttl\">\r\n            <p>\r\n              <span>キャリア紹介</span>\r\n            </p>\r\n          </div>\r\n          <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n            <div class=\"text\">\r\n              <p>入社以来、様々な部署を経験してきた先輩のキャリアステップを時系列に沿って紹介します。働く上で大切にしていること、当社で実現したい夢、様々な想いがつどう社員のキャリア紹介をご覧ください。</p>\r\n              <p class=\"img\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/sc.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_career.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n              <a href=\"job-people/career-index.html\" class=\"btn\">キャリア紹介</a></p>\r\n          </div>\r\n\r\n    </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"workstyle\">\r\n      <div class=\"inner c-flex__sb\">\r\n        <div class=\"ff\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff4.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n        <div class=\"text\">\r\n          <h2>\r\n            <img src=\"assets/img/index/ttl_workstyle.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            <span>働く環境を知る</span>\r\n          </h2>\r\n          <p>\r\n            豊かに働き、成長するための様々な制度についてご紹介します。\r\n          </p>\r\n          <ul class=\"pc\">\r\n            <li><a href=\"workstyle/welfare.html\" class=\"btn\">福利厚生／各種制度</a></li>\r\n            <li><a href=\"workstyle/training.html\" class=\"btn\">人財育成</a></li>\r\n          </ul>            \r\n        </div>\r\n        <p class=\"ph\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ph_work.png\" alt=\"\"></p>\r\n      </div>\r\n      <ul class=\"sp\">\r\n        <li><a href=\"workstyle/welfare.html\" class=\"btn\">福利厚生／各種制度</a></li>\r\n        <li><a href=\"workstyle/training.html\" class=\"btn\">人財育成</a></li>\r\n      </ul>            \r\n</section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"recruit\">\r\n      <div class=\"inner\">\r\n        <div class=\"ff\"><img src=\"assets/img/index/ff5.png\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n        <h2>\r\n          <img src=\"assets/img/index/ttl_recruit.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n          <span>採用情報</span>\r\n        </h2>\r\n        <ul class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n          <li><a href=\"recruit/index.html\" class=\"btn\">募集要項／採用担当者メッセージ</a></li>\r\n          <li><a href=\"recruit/faq.html\" class=\"btn\">よくあるご質問</a></li>\r\n        </ul>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </section>\r\n  </main>\r\n  \r\n  \r\n  <footer>\r\n    <div class=\"inner\">\r\n      <p id=\"flogo\"><a href=\"./\"><img src=\"assets/img/f_logo.png\" alt=\"株式会社キャリタス\"></a></p>\r\n      <div class=\"c-flex__sb\">\r\n        <dl>  \r\n          <dt>\r\n            <a href=\"https://mypage.3070.i-webs.jp/rec_ct2027/\" target=\"_blank\">新卒ENTRY／<br>MY PAGE</a>\r\n          </dt>  \r\n        </dl>\r\n        <dl class=\"fnavi1\">\r\n          <dt>\r\n            <img src=\"assets/img/f_navi01.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            <span>会社を知る</span>\r\n          </dt>\r\n          <dd>\r\n            <ul>\r\n              <li><a href=\"about/message.html\">トップメッセージ／<br>経営理念</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"about/business.html\">事業紹介</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </dd>\r\n        </dl>\r\n        <dl class=\"fnavi2\">\r\n          <dt>\r\n            <img src=\"assets/img/f_navi02.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            <span>仕事と人を知る</span>\r\n          </dt>\r\n          <dd>\r\n            <ul>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/work.html\">職種紹介</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/movie.html\">社員インタビュー</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/project01.html\">プロジェクトストーリー01</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/project02.html\">プロジェクトストーリー02</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/member.html\">日本全国地域を＋にするメンバー紹介</a></li>\r\n              <li><a href=\"job-people/career-index.html\">キャリア紹介</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n          </dd>\r\n        </dl>\r\n        <dl class=\"fnavi3\">\r\n          <dt>\r\n            <img src=\"assets/img/f_navi03.png\" alt=\"\">\r\n            <span>働く環境を知る</span>\r\n          </dt>\r\n          <dd>\r\n            <ul>\r\n              <li><a href=\"workstyle/welfare.html\">福利厚生／各種制度</a></li>\r\n        